text: Mianwali is a city in Punjab, Pakistan. Mianwali may also refer to: *Mianwali District, a district of Punjab (Pakistan). *Mianwali Tehsil, a tehsil of district Mianwali. *Mianwali Airport, a airport in Pakistan. *Mianwali railway station, a railway station in Pakistan. ==See also== *Mianwali Bangla, a village in Sailkot, Pakistan. *Mian Wali Qureshian, a village in Punjab, Pakistan. * *
title: Mianwali (disambiguation)
